665
00:37:11,145 --> 00:37:12,480
[Gerald] Mm-hmm.

666
00:37:30,581 --> 00:37:32,625
[director] Oh no.

667
00:37:32,708 --> 00:37:33,960
I'm sorry.

668
00:37:34,043 --> 00:37:35,086
- Like this?
- [laughter]

669
00:37:35,169 --> 00:37:37,213
[chuckles]

670
00:37:37,296 --> 00:37:38,756
[in English] Sorry.

671
00:37:38,839 --> 00:37:40,299
