- Oh no!
- [director] Oh no!

677
00:38:16,085 --> 00:38:17,295
Oh, I'm sorry!

678
00:38:17,378 --> 00:38:18,921
Is that bad?

679
00:38:19,005 --> 00:38:21,632
- [laughter]
- I'm sorry! Sorry!

680
