Sir, we received an alert.

681
00:38:41,777 --> 00:38:43,279
There's an active-- [stutters]

682
00:38:43,362 --> 00:38:45,573
There's an active
shooting in East-- [huffs]

683
00:38:45,656 --> 00:38:47,867
There's an active shooting
in East Valley-- [laughs]

684
00:38:47,950 --> 00:38:49,618
- [in English] Sorry.
- [in English] East Valley--

685
00:38:50,202 --> 00:38:52,580
- [laughter]
- [quirky sting]

686
00:38:53,247 --> 00:38:54,957
That name is so hard to say!

687
00:38:55,041 --> 00:38:56,917
[Felix] Agent Felix.

688
00:38:57,835 --> 00:38:58,836
[in English] It's good to meet you.

689
00:38:58,919 --> 00:39:01,547
